import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import React from 'react'
import App from './App'

import axios from 'axios'

const promise = axios
  .get('http://localhost:3001/notes')
  .then(response => {
    const notes = response.data
    console.log('Notes:', notes)

    ReactDOM.render(
      <App notes={notes} />,
      document.getElementById('root')
    )
  })
